- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper presents a computational procedure for finding exponential rate certificates.
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is also a possibility as the paper deals with finding numerical bounds on exponential decay rates.
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is less likely but still possible as the paper presents a computational procedure for finding exponential rate certificates in the context of engineering systems.
